            <thetext>Impossible to move messages between folders in mailboxes that have reached quota limit. That to move message mailbox should have not used quota in size of message. So in this case impossible to delete messages from overquoted mailbox because at first necessary to move messages to Trash folder.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
